The compiled app and the repository include or generate data files from third
parties under their own licences. See NOTICES for full attributions.

• assets/cities.tsv (and generated cities_precise.tsv, cities_detailed.tsv)
  Derived from GeoNames data © GeoNames — CC BY 4.0
  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/

• assets/ports.tsv (when generated by scripts/fetch_ports.py)
  Contains data from three sources:
  – World Port Index (NGA, US Government, Public Domain)
  – GeoNames harbour/marina data (CC BY 4.0)
  – OpenStreetMap contributors when --countries is used (ODbL 1.0)
  The generated file, if it contains OSM data, constitutes a Derived Database
  under the Open Database Licence 1.0 and must be redistributed under ODbL.
  https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1.0/
